<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink326">
<l>aḻalavir naṉantalai niḻaliṭam peṟātu</l>
<l>maṭamā ṉampiṇai maṟiyoṭu tiraṅka</l>
<l>nīrmaruṅ kaṟutta nirampā viyavi</l>
<l>ṉiṉṉā maṉṟa curamē</l>
<l>yiṉiya maṉṟayā ṉoḻintōḷ paṇpē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Indeed unpleasant is desert, </l>
<l>where in the riverbed with its sides eroded, and not filled with water, </l>
<l>beautiful doe of a foolish deer suffers from thirst with [its] fawn, </l>
<l>being unable to find shady place  </l>
<l>in the broad expanse, where heat is glowing.</l>
<l>And pleasant indeed are qualities of the girl I left behind. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
